{"tid":1361463,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"(附教學) 成功將藍絲呀媽改變成黃絲","createTime":"2019-07-24T15:16:50.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-26T02:32:34.000Z","uid":62648,"like":75,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"100c3b23e959931365c26ae9a9ed72e7f9040e9a","tid":1361463,"uid":62648,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T15:16:50.000Z","msg":"呀媽本身好撐警，又成日睇cctvb話啲學生搞事。但經過我日復日咁解釋佢聽，佢終於變左撐學生。總結我係用以下既方法：<br />\n<br />\n1. Facebook save/share多啲好有道理/好感人既文章，特別係啲寫比上一代個啲。然後讀比佢聽。<br />\n<br />\n2. 俾多啲黑警打人/高官比人插到口啞啞個啲片比佢睇，再係旁邊講述下。<br />\n<br />\n3. 轉睇now新聞，再同佢解釋邊啲邊啲畫面，佢係cctvb係永遠唔會睇到。<br />\n<br />\n4. 好似之前有個巴打咁講，用佢fb like返啲正常page，等佢接收返啲正常資訊。<br />\n<br />\n5. 打溫情牌。話而加啲人出黎都係為下一代，然後講多啲話你都唔想你啲孫仔孫女點點點。<br />\n<br />\n呀媽而加好撐學生<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n仲睇清楚高官真面目<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d6ab9a80c8eaa87241b854171d1e6fa81ca27049","tid":1361463,"uid":191290,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T15:17:09.000Z","msg":"借個位<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n【唔想輸嘅入嚟幫手置頂】如何避免被人鳩帶風向+攻破白色恐怖<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1361315\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1361315</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"161da9a80b38e5341aaed98657e36b3eeca86cda","tid":1361463,"uid":62648,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T15:24:02.000Z","msg":"好睇我舅父大舅個啲都係反政府人士<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n多方面夾攻我媽"},{"pid":"903d7e06bb5f2f01fa68ab3a91b2ff83cff722aa","tid":1361463,"uid":62648,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T15:32:47.000Z","msg":"推推推"},{"pid":"8b35cdacba0a6f0a29e53aced2af858b65cb97b3","tid":1361463,"uid":62648